    "Four fresh-frozen samples, adjacent slides with P3A_MBC, P3B_MBC, P4A_MBC and P4B_ MBC, were processed for PhenoCycler (CODEX) imaging in Enable Lab (https://www.enablemedicine.com).",
    "Samples were prepared and stained, and images were acquired following CODEX User Manual Rev C (https://www.akoyabio.com) at Enable Medicine.",
